{"tid":2247302,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西貢牛尾洲發現英軍炮彈","createTime":"2020-10-17T17:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T21:37:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f04e0334e6f9c795931e7adf3cb99c60f40576cd","tid":2247302,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:26:04.000Z","msg":"西貢牛尾洲再次驚現炸彈！上午8時許，一名40歲外籍男子報案表示，牛尾洲以西一石灘發現一枚懷疑炸彈，爆炸品處理課人員接報到場，於上址發現一枚直徑約3吋的英軍炮彈，之後在現場將該枚炸彈安全處理，事件中無人受傷，無須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n據悉回歸前，牛尾海的滘西洲、牛尾洲及吊鐘洲曾被列為牛尾海操炮區，供英軍操練。據了解，西貢牛尾洲一石灘於2011年亦出現一枚相信是70至80年代英製高爆迫擊炮彈，直徑約81毫米，長約45厘米。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201017/57B52K42LZGV7OLQ4YVUVXF7ZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201017%2F57B52K42LZGV7OLQ4YVUVXF7ZY%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=e145c7cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201017%2F57B52K42LZGV7OLQ4YVUVXF7ZY%2F&h=2fd9b55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201017/57B52K42LZGV7OLQ4YVUVXF7ZY/</a>"},{"pid":"d7f7bcc5273fd0ef175aee6bdaba5c132cd9fa71","tid":2247302,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1732485610b593c847db3fc9061e040fb6ed1933","tid":2247302,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7f7bcc5273fd0ef175aee6bdaba5c132cd9fa71","tid":2247302,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17